phsp - Phitherek_' s Startup Profiler - Installation

1. Dependencies
phsp-conf-gtk needs a GTK+-2.0 or later library (development to compile and runtime to work) and pkg-config command for compilation. All the rest needs only the build environment (this one from GNU) for C++.
2. make
Compiles phsp (Profile Launcher), phsp-conf (Config Tool) and phsp-conf-gtk (GTK Config Tool).
3. make install (with root privileges by sudo)
Sets up phsp for active user and installs the program into /usr/bin and additional files to /usr/share/phsp.
4. (optional) make userset
Sets up phsp for active user. This can be done also by /usr/share/phsp/phsp-userset script after installation.
